channel.title: Dev looking for a server
channel.description:
I'm a java developer with lots of experience i'm looking to join and develop on a rsps.
Benefits:
- I'm experienced about 10 years in java. - I'm very versatile be it a website you want to have your npcs move about to setting up sql for your server i can pretty much do it all or at least learn what i need to to get by fairly quickly. - I'm free i do this for fun basically logging in as some unknown "Hacker" and making all the npcs dance and sing... just the looks on their faces will be payment enough. - I'm really looking to get onboard with a fun server i can tinker with in the past i have tried creating my own rsps servers unfortunately i always had trouble getting a player base if i join your server and if you have good player flow and if it is fun for me i will most likely donate to the server on a regular basis depending on how much fun im having this may even include large donations yes im speaking sponsorships.
Skype: project.demon
